(hy pWfy!) prmwqmw (qyry) nyVy (Bwv, ihrdy ivc v`s irhw) hY, aus nUM (Awpxy qoN dUr nwh smJ, iek prmwqmw hI swrI isRStI ivc mOjUd hY[
hy nwnk! iek srb-ivAwpk prmwqmw hI (hr QW) smwieAw hoieAw hY, aus qoN ibnw koeI hor dUjw nhIN hY ]5]
