mwieAw dy mqvwly jIv nUM (jd qk) JUT ny Tg-bUtI cmoVI hoeI hY,
(jd qk jIv) csky ivc lwlc ivc qy prweI muQwjI ivc ^uAwr ho irhw hY, qd qk hr vyly ies nUM hwhukw hI hwhukw hY[
