auh mnu`K suK mwxdw hY, ijs mnu`K nUM pRBU AwpxI myhr nwl ieh dwq dyNdw hY
Aqy ijs nUM gurU dI rwhIN (AwpxI srb-ivAwpkqw dw aupdyS) suxWdw hY ]7]
(hy pWfy! aus gopwl dw nwm Awpxy mn dI p`tI auqy ilK), DrqI Aqy AkwS ivc ijs dI joiq dw prkwS hY,
jo sB qoN v`fw gopwl iqMn BvnW ivc ivAwpk hY[
auh gopwl AwpxI ikrpw kr ky (gurU dI rwhIN) prgt ho ky ijs nUM Awpxw (srb-ivAwpk) srUp ivKWdw hY,
auh mnu`K (Btkxw qoN bc ky) Awpxy Awp ivc itk jWdw hY[
jgq nUM sohxw bnwx vwlw pRBU (ijs mnu`K dy ihrdy ivc) nyVy ho ky (AwpxI is&q-swlwh dI) JVI lw ky vrHdw hY,
auh mnu`K siqgurU dy sRySt Sbd dI rwhIN (jgq nUM svwrxhwr)-
ies pRBU dw ieh Byq jwx lYNdw hY,
ik pRBU Awp hI swry jgq dw pYdw krn vwlw hY qy Awp hI (Awp joiq nwl ies nUM) cwnx dyx vwlw hY (Bwv, pRBU Awp hI ies jgq nUM jIvn-rwh isKwx vwlw) hY ]8]
